\&\s-1COLORS\s0 \- A hash reference or a file name
.Sp
.Vb 10
\&        {
\&        HTML =>
\&                {
\&                white => "color:#888;",
\&                black => "color:#000;",
\&                ...
\&                }
\&        ANSI => ...
\&        ASCII => ...
\&        }
.Ve
.PP
\&\fIReturns\fR \- Text::Colorizer
.PP
\&\fIExceptions\fR \- Dies if the color description are not valid
